{"tid":874024,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（剛需代表）人大代表王敏剛借款1.55億買樓","createTime":"2018-10-24T01:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T13:37:14.000Z","uid":50457,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4e65cbb6dcaa670e8f25b724cf1e028a68fd4793","tid":874024,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T01:18:58.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】新鴻基公司（0086）發公告指，旗下的新鴻基信貸向新鴻基公司獨立非執行董事王敏剛（圖）訂立貸款協議，向王借出3筆貸款，合共1.55億元，當中1000萬元的短期貸款，年利率達18厘，期限為6個月，公告提到，這筆短期貸款中一半會用於購買深水灣住宅物業的按金及部分付款，另一半會用作繳付印花稅。<br />\n1000萬元短期貸款 年息達18厘<br />\n<br />\n第二筆貸借為1.15億元的分期貸款，期限為12個月， 第一期利率為每年19.625厘，第二至第十二期為每年7.625厘，公告指，王敏剛會將上述分期貸款用作支付該深水灣住宅物業的購買價餘額。第三筆貸借為3000萬元，期限為12個月，年利率7.625厘，用作悉數償還上述1000萬元的短期貸款。<br />\n<br />\n王敏剛為「船王」王華生之子，為港區全國人大代表，並在多家香港上市公司擔任董事，包括遠東發展（0035）、美高梅中國（2282）、信和酒店（1221）等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181024/s00004/1540319551228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181024%2Fs00004%2F1540319551228&d=0%2BfN0%2FGWhSQDVPNeac0z7JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b700a543\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181024%2Fs00004%2F1540319551228&h=34a3ceeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181024/s00004/1540319551228</a>"},{"pid":"fa355d79edcd6ea82629509eb02e33215af76413","tid":874024,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"6個月短期貸款18厘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該非常睇好後市"},{"pid":"f9331fc82184bf3467b6cfed5150211bdb4a7200","tid":874024,"uid":203322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"真正剛需"},{"pid":"9718a139952b0f20ee2d22b263757f5f621